metadata.name: Dickbutt Balloon (mid/red)
metadata.description:
Two of the most iconic memes in history come together again. 

Dickbutt and Nyan Cat. 

Both wildly popular on their own, they do share a certain history together as well.

They first joined forces as NFTs in the CryptoDickbutt OG collection with token #158 minted on March 24th, 2021, paying homage to Nyan Cat by combining elements of both collections into a single gif. It's essentially a gray Dickbutt body with cat ears, rosy cheeks, holding a cherry pop-tart... and I'm pretty sure that's not a tail back there lol. It's seen flying through space leaving a rainbow trail in its wake. Pure bliss for meme lovers.

Both of these legendary internet memes were brought to life in web3 as NFTs within days of one another in early March of 2021. With the recent release of Nyan Balloon, I was inspired to reconnect the icons for a small limited edition combining an S3 CryptoDickbutt and the Nyan Balloon style sky and animation, with a couple of small tweaks to things. iykyk 

There will be no burn or game or ponzi or raffle or double dutch scavenger hunt reveal mechanic.

69 free for CryptoDickbutt holders  
69 free for Nyan Cat holders  
420 for public minting for .0069  
42 to give away  
600 total

This will not make you rich.  
This will not make me rich.  
It's a fun nft, that's it. 

I hope everyone enjoys thiers.


And very special thanks to @whoaslowbro and @PRguitarman  
for bringing so much joy into the world with your skills, creativity, and imaginations.
